### 2.3 Automation tokens
#### 2.3.1 create automation token (== project-scope)
POST https://localhost:8080/api/v1/projects/{{project}}/roles/{{role}}/token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Token for sample-test-project and sample-test-project-role"
}

### 2.3.2 -- NOTHING returned, because there is NO Application / sample-test-project-related
GET https://localhost:8080/api/v1/applications
#Authorization: Bearer <PREVIOUS_ROLE_TOKEN_2.3.1>
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpc3MiOiJhcmdvY2QiLCJzdWIiOiJwcm9qOnNhbXBsZS10ZXN0LXByb2plY3Q6c2FtcGxlLXRlc3QtcHJvamVjdC1yb2xlIiwibmJmIjoxNzc3OTk3OTkxLCJpYXQiOjE3Nzc5OTc5OTEsImp0aSI6IjBkOTBhZmIyLTAzZGQtNGE3OC05Yjc1LWI3OWZhNmVhNWE2ZCJ9.NvzDTF4kAKOSJLRUaUhJTMKEIwv82_Dq5z7BBbj3QNw

### 2.3.3 -- privilege-limited (== role-related) -- can NOT delete it
DELETE https://localhost:8080/api/v1/projects/{{project}}
Content-Type: application/json
#Authorization: Bearer <PREVIOUS_ROLE_TOKEN_2.3.1>
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpc3MiOiJhcmdvY2QiLCJzdWIiOiJwcm9qOnNhbXBsZS10ZXN0LXByb2plY3Q6c2FtcGxlLXRlc3QtcHJvamVjdC1yb2xlIiwibmJmIjoxNzc3OTk3OTkxLCJpYXQiOjE3Nzc5OTc5OTEsImp0aSI6IjBkOTBhZmIyLTAzZGQtNGE3OC05Yjc1LWI3OWZhNmVhNWE2ZCJ9.NvzDTF4kAKOSJLRUaUhJTMKEIwv82_Dq5z7BBbj3QNw

#### 2.3.4  create automation token / configurable expiration
POST https://localhost:8080/api/v1/projects/{{project}}/roles/{{role}}/token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Token for sample-test-project and sample-test-project-role with configurable expiration",
  "expiresIn": 120
}

### 2.3.5   if you want to revoke IMMEDIATELY -> delete the JWT reference ID | project role
DELETE https://localhost:8080/api/v1/projects/{{project}}/roles/{{role}}/token/{{iat}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. Sensitive information
### 3.1 NEVER returns sensitive data -- from -- its API
GET https://localhost:8080/api/v1/repocreds
#Authorization: Bearer <PREVIOUS_ROLE_TOKEN_2.3.1>
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 3.2 -- sanitize/hide ALL sensitive data | API payloads & logs --
GET https://localhost:8080/api/v1/clusters
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

